SOLARIS ARCHIVE MANAGER TESTS
=============================

Safety
------

The test will neither change the user's file, nor change the system file, it only extracts some test files to system /tmp/ folder. They are safe to run. For the archive test, the new created tar.gz file will be removed after each test case finishes.

Configurations
------

The tests don't need any special configuarations.

Available Tests
------

* Create a .tar.gz file from a text file
* Create a .tar.gz file from a png file
* Create a .tar.gz file from a wav file
* Create a .tar.gz file from a pdf file
* Create a .tar.gz file from a specified folder
* Extract a specified .tar.gz file to /tmp/ folder
